<br>
So, the best stuff you can get is blue diamond gear.<br>
<br>
2 BD bracers<br>
2 BD earrings<br>
2 velium jacinth rings (+14 MR each)<br>
SBS (+10 MR/CR/FR)<br>
Froggy crown (20 FR/CR)<br>
Supple scale wristband +10 FR (not sure if pallies can wear, common no drop in KC)<br>
Drakescale belt +10 FR<br>
Cloak of the Ice Bear +20 CR<br>
Earring of Essence +10 MR<br>
Gold Diamond Mask +10 CR/FR +3 MR <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uglorianafrostglitter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gloriana Frostglitter</A> at: 2/5/02 11:11:07 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/unogem.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nogem</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/misc_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 507<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/5/02 11:25:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8572.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Any Ideas on Gear</span><hr size=1> I'd like to add runed bone fork to Gloriana's list, 10fr 10mr 10cr. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cullomthapally>CullomThaPally</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/6/02 12:40:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8572.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Any Ideas on Gear</span><hr size=1> Theres not a way i can afford BD stuff though hehe<br>
